1
00:00:58,080 --> 00:01:03,400
A mysterious group lives in the Dayin Dynasty.

2
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:07,080
They are born with special abilities.

3
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:08,200
Eagle vision,

4
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:09,640
invisibility,

5
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,260
and earth-tunneling.

6
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:15,320
They are mutants different from ordinary people.

7
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:17,320
Among them,

8
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,920
a branch of the Helian clan,

9
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,960
due to their skill in finding gold

10
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,280
and gold mines,

11
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:23,720
were reduced to gold mine slaves.

12
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,039
The Shen clan, born with eagle vision and skilled in archery,

13
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,960
formed the Shenji Camp.

14
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:33,400
Half of the world's mutants belonged to it.

15
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:37,039
The royal Ji clan feared their power.

16
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:39,440
To uproot the Shen family's influence,

17
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:42,880
the elderly emperor forced the Shen family's only daughter,

18
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:45,009
Shen Mingyue, to marry him as empress.

19
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:47,440
He bestowed the royal surname Ji upon her

20
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:51,240
to cut off the Shen family's lineage.

21
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:34,520
The gold embezzlement case implicates the entire Dayin court.

22
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,960
Now that the ledger is in my hands,

23
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,800
many people will surely be on pins and needles.

24
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:44,040
Could the ledger for the gold case be on her?

25
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:55,920
Newcomer?

26
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:58,880
Yes.

27
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,090
One of Mother's people.

28
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,440
What did she ask you to do?

29
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,840
The gold case concerns the Northern Border and the Crown Prince.

30
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:34,440
The Crown Prince is already watching you with the crystal stone.

31
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:54,720
The Shen family's Eagle Eye is indeed impressive.

32
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,240
Greetings, Your Highness.

33
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,120
I wonder if the matter of the ledger

34
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,560
is known to Ji Hongzhen.

35
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:17,399
Ji Hongzhen, I already have the ledger of the gold case.

36
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,060
Once I find out your connection to this case,

37
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,000
even if you are the Crown Prince.

38
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,120
Even your father can't protect you.

39
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,120
Get out.

40
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,280
Yes.

41
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,520
Get out.

42
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,880
Smells good.

43
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,760
You may step down too.

44
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,880
Yes.

45
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,640
Mother, you are so uninhibited.

46
00:04:57,640 --> 00:05:01,840
You completely disregard past affections and the royal family's dignity.

47
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:04,060
Do you think my father is dead?

48
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:07,320
Your father is now bedridden with a stroke.

49
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,980
What's the difference between that and being dead?

50
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,200
Right.

51
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,460
You are in your prime, Mother.

52
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,520
If you are too lonely to bear,

53
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,320
why not come to me?

54
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,760
If they can do it,

55
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:24,840
why can't I?

56
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,540
As long as your father is still alive,

57
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,160
you will always be the Crown Prince.

58
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,360
And I will always be your mother.

59
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,159
What a pity.

60
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:41,090
You won't be my mother much longer.

61
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:52,300
Do you think you can beat your father?

62
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,440
How would I know without trying?

63
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,440
Assassin!

64
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,680
Guards!

65
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,920
No matter how you struggle,

66
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,080
or how unwilling you are,

67
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,600
you will end up being my woman.

68
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,640
You can't escape.

69
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,720
Ji Hongzhen,

70
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,180
don't forget your status.

71
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,800
You are the Crown Prince,

72
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,930
and I am the Empress.

73
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,840
If you dare to barge into my bedchamber casually

74
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,520
and speak so insolently again,

75
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,800
next time, my arrow

76
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,360
will aim for your head.

77
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,060
Your Highness,

78
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:55,320
His Majesty was prepared.

79
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,300
This old bastard is really tough to kill.

80
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,120
Give orders for tonight's plan.

81
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,760
If there are any more mistakes,

82
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,600
you don't have to come back.

83
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,640
Yes.

84
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,640
Ji Mingyue.

85
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:16,160
There is no woman I want

86
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,640
that I cannot have.

87
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:22,020
The Crown Prince has always coveted you.

88
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,800
But you are his mother in name.

89
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,520
He

90
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,440
is truly a madman.

91
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,880
Thankfully, you adopted the Ninth Prince as soon as you entered the palace,

92
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,720
which has spared you a lot of trouble.

93
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,200
It's just too unfair to you.

94
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:34,400
The royal family fears the Shen family.

95
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:36,370
That's why the Emperor married me.

96
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:39,260
If the Shen family doesn't yield,

97
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,640
and if the General's Manor loses its power,

98
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,920
the Divine Machine Camp, which relies on us to survive,

99
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,640
will immediately become

100
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:48,440
ravenous wolves turning against the Shen family.

101
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,800
I understand.

102
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:51,880
But this

103
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,600
is too unfair to you.

104
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,120
In this world,

105
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,240
where is there any fairness?

106
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,440
Strange.

107
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:07,010
Why is the smoke from this censer so heavy?

108
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,860
The Huo family,

109
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,360
the Northern Frontier,

110
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,120
Ji Hongzhen,

111
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,600
and the Helian clan involved in gold mining...

112
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,120
It seems a storm is brewing in Great Yin.

113
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,240
Go invite Huo Lingyu.

114
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,770
I have something to ask her.

115
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,640
Yes.

116
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,240
How dare you show off such a trivial invisibility spell

117
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,160
in front of me?

118
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:40,840
The eyes break through all obstacles,

119
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:43,040
and the magic weapon breaks through all spells.

120
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:45,440
The weapon forged by Shen's Magic Weapon Camp

121
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,770
is indeed the natural enemy of strangers.

122
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,840
The magic weapon breaks through all spells.

123
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:03,040
Your Highness, you've been hit by my immobilizing spell.

124
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,460
How should I break this spell?

125
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:13,300
I must find the account book quickly.

126
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,640
Otherwise,

127
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:18,810
I'm afraid I won't be able to return to the Northern Realm alive.

128
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,730
I've searched everywhere,

129
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,060
but I couldn't find the account book.

130
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,720
It should be on her.

131
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,400
I don't want to do anything,

132
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,000
just looking for something.

133
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,240
You found me so quickly.

134
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,560
I wonder whose subordinate you are.

135
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,400
It seems I guessed right.

136
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:03,060
You are indeed here for the account book.

137
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,560
You can actually break my immobilizing spell?

138
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,600
No,

139
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,480
it doesn't look like Shen's spell.

140
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,240
My subordinates will be here soon.

141
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,700
I'll give you three moves.

142
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,050
Within three moves,

143
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,320
if you can't take me down,

144
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,280
I'll kill you.

145
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,000
I never wanted your life.

146
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:52,120
Why are your moves so aggressive?

147
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,780
Otherwise,

148
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:56,760
should I give you another chance to cast the immobilizing spell?

149
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,640
Excuse me.

150
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,720
You lecher,

151
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,640
you're so shameless.

152
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:21,040
The incense burner has been tampered with.

153
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,560
Ji Hongzhen, that bastard.

154
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,440
Wushan Xing.

155
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:36,360
The poisoned person will lose all their spells within the time it takes an incense stick to burn.

156
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,240
They will die if they are not detoxified.

157
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,640
What kind of move is this?

158
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,880
Oh no,

159
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:03,450
this medicine triggered the Qianji poison in my body to flare up early.

160
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,450
With the two poisons combined,

161
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,330
I'm afraid I'll die here today.

162
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:09,920
So hot.

163
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:07,360
Hurry!

164
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,740
His Highness ordered,

165
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,280
we must find Her Highness.

166
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:13,440
Hurry,

167
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,720
search here too.

168
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:17,720
Hurry!

169
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:38,890
They all say I'm a bewitching demon queen.

170
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,280
No matter who this person is,

171
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,080
it's going to be true this time.
